data.description: Welcome to this charming home built in 2015, offering a perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless appeal. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom property is located in a peaceful and well-established neighborhood, offering both comfort and convenience. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere, with an open-concept layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The spacious living room's natural light, creates a relaxing space for family gatherings or entertaining guests. The fully-equipped kitchen boasts contemporary finishes, with ample cabinet space. The master bedroom is a tranquil retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom for added privacy. The two additional bedrooms are generously sized and share a well-appointed second bathroom, ideal for accommodating family members or guests. Additional features of this wonderful home include a two-car garage, energy-efficient appliances, central heating, and cooling to ensure year-round comfort, and a laundry area for added convenience. Located in a family-friendly community of Stonewood Estates, you'll have easy access to local schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes, making daily commutes a breeze. If you're looking for a lovingly-maintained home with modern features and a welcoming ambiance, you may call this one HOME. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house yourHome Sweet Home!
